        {
            "title": "警尖沙咀截可疑車檢「冰」毒及太空油 25歲女及35歲男友被捕",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"警方於尖沙咀山林道截獲毒品快餐車。黎志偉攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/d97c6acb0cddebe1d2446c905fa030c6/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250329/_2025032905095062695.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">警方於尖沙咀山林道截獲毒品快餐車。黎志偉攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>警方尖沙咀截獲毒品車。今日（29日）凌晨3時許，西九龍機動部隊人員在山林道巡邏期間，發現一輛停泊在咪錶位的藍色Audi私家車上，一男一女坐在後座，警員察覺有可疑遂上前調查。\n\n</p>\n<p>搜查期間，警員在私家車後座檢獲一個黑色手提袋，袋內臟有6粒「太空油」、一包懷疑「冰」毒及「冰」壼，警員遂將車上35歲男子及25歲女子拘捕，隨後帶返警署作進一步調查。毒品重量和價值仍在點算。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4164678/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警員到場調查。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f5186c996eab5df41155176af2510705/2025-03/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-03-29-04-20-24_002.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警員到場調查。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4164679/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"35歲男子被捕。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c70ae54ae9c9e60b2acebebc4a7766f9/2025-03/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-03-29-04-21-01_014.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        35歲男子被捕。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4164680/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警方拘捕一名25歲女子。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e333f751ff4ed545ed6cc018ed20babd/2025-03/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-03-29-04-20-58_013.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警方拘捕一名25歲女子。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4164681/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警員在山林道截獲可疑私家車。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/66476f6b4e7ff21b87a743f2b0c9ab1d/2025-03/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-03-29-04-20-44_008.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警員在山林道截獲可疑私家車。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4164682/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警員在車內檢獲懷疑毒品。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/93cda2290ff1a37cd622a29e38f75382/2025-03/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-03-29-04-20-47_009.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警員在車內檢獲懷疑毒品。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>據了解，兩人報稱任職待應，為情侶關係。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
