            "title": "緬甸地震︱曼德勒皇宮塔樓倒塌 萬塔之城蒲甘寺廟損毀",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"曼德勒皇宮塔樓傾斜，萬塔之城蒲甘寺廟損毀。\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/47a896e805f527029adb5de6c3f98b4a/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250329/_2025032902203937992.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">曼德勒皇宮塔樓傾斜，萬塔之城蒲甘寺廟損毀。</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p></p><p dir=\"ltr\">緬甸實皆省（Sagaing）西北部週五（28日）下午時分發生7.9級地震，國內多處損毀，至少造成144人死亡，數百人受傷。在震央附近的曼德勒省內有多處建築受損，包括曼德勒皇宮及被列為世界文化遺產的蒲甘古城。\n\n</p><h2 dir=\"ltr\">曼德勒皇宮嚴重受損</h2>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">據今日緬甸（Myanmar Now ) 報道，位於曼德勒的曼德勒皇宮嚴重受損，包包括皇宮內部的宮牆和一棟建築也倒塌。曼德勒皇宮於1857至1859年興建，為緬甸最後一個王朝「貢榜王朝」的宮殿，是該王朝最後兩位國王、敏東國王和錫袍國王的主要住所。\n\n</p><p dir=\"ltr\">從網上的圖片可見，皇宮的外牆有部分倒塌，有磚塊剥落；皇宮內一個塔樓出現傾則，皇宮在地震後塵土飛揚。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4164652/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"地震後曼德勒皇宮外牆倒塌。網圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e84a4ec49d7949fb58f270d96d4780dc/2025-03/487198354_949498527394891_6450816240274991281_n.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        地震後曼德勒皇宮外牆倒塌。網圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4164653/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"地震後曼德勒皇宮外牆倒塌。網圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ccd96bc74da28060f1d1126e67119c92/2025-03/487492180_949498437394900_52686700101558129_n.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        地震後曼德勒皇宮外牆倒塌。網圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4164654/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"曼德勒皇宮一塔樓在地震後傾斜。網圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/89976a631b0b23ed5b969623dbfe4413/2025-03/487496266_949498417394902_753966627537032356_n.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        曼德勒皇宮一塔樓在地震後傾斜。網圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4164655/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"曼德勒皇宮原貌。Alamy\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0503ca4a52cd6c6531e5883b509a8fd8/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-28_at_18_08_40_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        曼德勒皇宮原貌。Alamy\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4164656/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"曼德勒皇宮原貌。Alamy\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/37d434c4d742bc1991efbe166bb19e44/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-28_at_18_08_40.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        曼德勒皇宮原貌。Alamy\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2 dir=\"ltr\">蒲甘古城一片頹垣敗瓦</h2>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">另外，在曼德勒省西部的蒲甘王國古城，在地震中同樣受到嚴重損毀。從一段網上片段中可見，古城中的佛塔結構受嚴重，磚塊散落在地上，外牆倒塌，現場一片頹垣敗瓦，滿目瘡痍。一個金色的寺廁頂部尖塔亦倒塌。在古城外擺賣的攤檔貨物散落一地，商販及部分兒童情色慌張，疑地震仍有餘悸。\n\n</p><p dir=\"ltr\">蒲甘（Bagan）是緬甸最著名的古城之一，擁有多座壯觀的佛塔，被譽為「萬塔之城」。蒲甘曾是蒲甘王朝的首都，是緬甸最早統一的王國，也是當時東南亞最輝煌的佛教文化中心之一，在2019 年被列為聯合國教科文組織世界遺產。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4164657/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"男童地震後仍有餘悸。網片截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6e6a5d8a53079defa97006042ff08d0f/2025-03/2025-03-29_02_10_01.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        男童地震後仍有餘悸。網片截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4164658/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"蒲甘古城一片頹垣敗瓦，滿目瘡痍。網片截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/97529bd2c3dbd9902743f8d31ce14a89/2025-03/2025-03-29_02_10_04.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        蒲甘古城一片頹垣敗瓦，滿目瘡痍。網片截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4164659/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"寺廟塔頂倒塌。網片截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/29f459c8d386d823d652b7cd8c5afde6/2025-03/2025-03-29_02_10_21.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        寺廟塔頂倒塌。網片截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4164660/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"蒲甘古城一片頹垣敗瓦，滿目瘡痍。網片截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1b980d1eea1bea1aaf07e3cd1a2d7727/2025-03/2025-03-29_02_10_37.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        蒲甘古城一片頹垣敗瓦，滿目瘡痍。網片截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4164661/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"蒲甘古城原貌。Alamy\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e4b69ca3a536893ff04f4a0b038fed6a/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-28_at_17_59_10.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        蒲甘古城原貌。Alamy\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
