            "title": "太古城中心二期中年男子高處墮下 送院搶救後不治",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"太古城中心二期中年男子高處墮下，送院搶救後不治。\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/8a56807761c85a27cbe52fa98e5951ca/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250328/_2025032900040822168.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">太古城中心二期中年男子高處墮下，送院搶救後不治。</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>太古城發生墮樓案。周五（28日）晚上近7時許，警方接獲途人報案，指發現一名男子倒臥在太古城中心2期2樓平台。救援人員接報到場，發現男事主陷入昏迷，他被送往東區尤德夫人那打素醫院治理，其後被證實死亡。\n\n</p>\n<p>警方經初步調查，相信該名年約40至50歲男子，疑從商場一樓層墮下。警方於現場沒有檢獲遺書。死因有待驗屍後確定。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4164627/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"太古城中心二期中年男子高處墮下，送院搶救後不治。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3705276feb167b29798f932283f81c34/2025-03/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-03-28-23-54-26_0.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        太古城中心二期中年男子高處墮下，送院搶救後不治。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
